metadata.title: Multichannel Seismic-Reflection Data  Navarin Basin-Northern Bering Sea-Alaska USGS Open File Report 86-207

creators.name: Atmospheric Administration (NOAA), National Environmental Satellite, Data
Information Service (NESDIS), National Geophysical Data Center (NGDC)

metadata.description:
Approximately 3,200-km of 24-channel seismic-reflection
profile data across the continental margin in the northeastern
Bering Sea are available for purchase from the National
Geophysical Data Center (NGDC) .  These profiles were provided to
NGDC for public dissemination by the U.S. Geological Survey, U.S.
Department of Interior.  This data set has 12 seismic lines (20
sections).
